('79100','27348','5','Beautiful country house in the Sierra de Tramuntana'),
('79101','27349','5','In the midst of the wild romantic landscape of the Sierra de Tramuntana, in a small and peaceful village you will find this lovely country house, which is in a perfect condition.\r\nThis house offers seven spacious, lovely decorated bedrooms, all equipped with en suite bathrooms. The house features air conditioning, central heating and satellite television. The luxurious rooms are tastefully decorated in Mediterranean style, reflecting the charm of old Spain. The original building, with two Moorish towers, has been carefully restored by local craftsmen, maintaining its traditional character, while a modern and elegant ambience is provided. \r\nFurthermore, the property disposes of a spacious apartment with living room, two bedrooms and bathroom. Outside you will find a beautifully kept Mediterranean garden and a swimming pool with surrounding sun terraces.\r\nThe property has been used as a country hotel until now.'),
